Detailed Description

Choose the structure based on the EventID received.

  • Use CatEventIDDataTlv if the Event ID is any of the below.
    • 16
    • 17
    • 18
    • 19
    • 20
    • 23
    • 24
  • Use CatAlPhaIdentifierTlv if the Event ID is 21
  • Use CatEventListTlv if the Event ID is 22
  • Use CatRefreshTlv if the Event ID is 25
  • Use CatEndProactiveSessionTlv if the Event ID is 26
